  <color="#fff06a"><bgcolor="#000000">❖OpenAI Image API Console

<color><bgcolor>  <color="#ffffff"><bgcolor="#000000">We developed a desktop tool for operating OpenAI image generation
<color><bgcolor>  <color="#ffffff"><bgcolor="#000000">and editing APIs. Built with Tauri / React / Vite, it supports
<color><bgcolor>  <color="#ffffff"><bgcolor="#000000">text-to-image generation, input images, mask editing, transparent
<color><bgcolor>  <color="#ffffff"><bgcolor="#000000">PNG output, quality settings, and local history.
<color><bgcolor>  <color="#ffffff"><bgcolor="#000000">It is available for macOS, Windows, and Linux.

